parameters: It seems there are no traps in this area.

I thought the leader of this organization would be here...
Maybe they've gone somewhere.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]This is perfect timing, let's disable the barrier while we
can.

Yeah, it seems right. Just wait a moment, I'll try to
disable the barrier.

I just wanted to be with you, big sis... so I followed
you...

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Oh my, you say such cute things. But it's dangerous, so you
can't wander around alone, okay?

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Soon I'll be able to call for our friends, so just wait a
little longer.
I think this should disable the barrier.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[9]Then I just need to release my spiritual power with all my
might, right?!
Don't push yourself until we arrive... huh...

It's no use. I've changed the channel for spiritual power
communication.
[EX]セルフスイッチタイプ = A

I never thought we could communicate through spiritual
power, but thanks to that, I've enjoyed quite the
entertaining diversion.
Yes, I'm also the director here...
I go by the name Liberator [Belial].

Watching your fight served as a benchmark to gauge the
Guardians' strength, and it also allowed me to replenish the
spiritual power needed for our operations.

Exactly, and thanks to you calling the Guardians here, I was
able to save myself the trouble of declaring war.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]So I was dancing in the palm of your hand...
Now... let's discuss... How about joining us?

Just listen. You're a power user, so you understand, right?
The frustration of only being able to use your abilities
within the rules set by the Guardians.

We aim to free power users from those rules so they can
freely use their abilities.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]So that's why you call yourselves Liberators.
What's wrong with power users freely using their abilities!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]All for the sake of the \C[2]Guardians' Annihilation
Plan\C[0]...

That's right. We'll eliminate the Guardians who unjustly
suppress power users and create a world where those born
with 'power' can freely use it!

How about it? Don't you want to use your 'power' whenever
and as much as you like?

...I see... then there's no helping it. You've served your
purpose well enough, so I'll ask you to exit the stage here.
This is... for the best, right...?

Well done, Amy. Even the formidable magical girl was
completely off guard.

Seraphiel... The next time I see you, the Guardians might
already be annihilated. Hahahaha!!
